description:
A basic 101 introduction to the Algebra – II.

Includes following topics:

Polynomial Basics,
Polynomial Division,
Synthetic Division,
Factoring Polynomials,
Linear Algebra,
Matrix Applications,
Linear Inequalities,
Linear Equations and Functions,
Linear Inequalities and Graphs,
Logarithms,
Absolute Value,
Sequences and Series,
Counting,
Probability,
Complex Numbers,
Conic Sections,
Circle and Parabola,
Ellipse and Hyperbola,
Quadratic Equations,
Formula Pack.
